Hello Isparian, my name is Aun Teverea.  All Tumeroks in the xuta of Aun Hareltah have been invited to join the new alliance.

We are assigned to this outpost near Wai Jhou, to collect building materials for the continued upkeep of Candeth Keep, the South Direlands stronghold. I will accept all types of cloth and hide that you can afford to donate to the cause.  Large or small, your donations will be treated equally.

Would you care to provide us with more materials? I accept all types of salvaged hide and cloth that you can afford to donate to the cause.
Welcome back, your continued help is most welcome! Any salvaged hide and cloth you can donate is greatly appreciated.
StrongholdTumerokBuilder
StrongholdTumerokBuilder@1
Thank you friend.  It takes many skins to build the tents and lean-to's we Tumeroks use in Candeth Keep.
You are off to a very good start. Yet, building materials are still in short supply. Please continue to bring me what you can.  If only Wharu had a salvageable hide...
Ah, more materials for the stronghold.  The reedshark, the armoredillo, and even the auroch have provided us the resources needed to survive in these harsh lands.
You have given me one-half the hide and cloth materials that I would ask of you. The residents of Candeth Keep shall know you by your name and your deeds.

Tell Many of the hide and cloth materials you have donated are now being cut and prepared for transport to Candeth Keep. With the harsh conditions and powerful creatures in the South Dires they can always use the new material supplies.  Your efforts shall be rewarded.
You have given much to help the alliance.  More materials are still needed, but rest assured you have donated the bulk of the quota set forth by the alliance council.

The storehouses are beginning to fill with the materials you and the others have generously given to the cause.  We now have enough materials to make another delivery to Candeth Keep, but we will surely need more to maintain our stronghold.
Friend, your hard work has paid off.  You have given the most that can be donated by any one member.
You will be welcomed in Candeth Keep as a co-founder.  Your donations of cloth and animal hide will not go unrewarded.
If you would like to be known as a skilled trapper, return this token to me.
Take this animal for your head. It keeps you warm on cold nights of hunting.
